{"tid":1535050,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"請唔好再討論警狗每日記招","createTime":"2019-09-03T08:12:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T11:07:36.000Z","uid":24178,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"420f38ec2ebd4c4a6dac872bdc1f82e173f4e737","tid":1535050,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:12:27.000Z","msg":"依家每日都好多濫捕好多警暴<br />\n佢個所謂記招只係係到發放藍絲文宣<br />\n佢播果啲片同你啲藍絲屋企人share 果啲有咩分別<br />\n頭一個禮拜都仲叫會答下記者提問<br />\n依家基本上只係錄音機<br />\n<br />\n佢9up 完啲大話大家又係到揾料rebut 佢 變左佢做主動<br />\n我地有手足會好上心去揾證據去反佢只會被佢帶住走<br />\n<br />\n我地不如專心做好手頭上既野<br />\n<br />\n班狗up 咩關我撚事咩<br />\n冷處理 做好我地既文宣<br />\n<br />\n以後有人再同你講嘩班狗今日話 xxx 好痴線啊 咁講都有<br />\n直接覆佢，關我撚事"},{"pid":"16a0cd298e5d009e8f76898d53cdc78be62e1a25","tid":1535050,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:12:37.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31cf28d8d5fce58440bad067c31476e9153312dc","tid":1535050,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:15:58.000Z","m